{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"69f423a2de","title":"毛泽东元旦祝词","origin":"原载一九五二年一月三日《人民日报》。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"de2f1f9759","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":1,"articleId":"69f423a2de"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9a088a5000","type":"title","text":"毛泽东元旦祝词","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"04cf01184e","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"6c33d4eb46","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们全体--人民政府的工作人员，人民志愿军和人民解放军的指挥员、战斗员，各民主党派，各人民团体，各少数民族和全国人民，在各个工作战线上的胜利!","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"13502ade60","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在抗美援朝战线上的胜利!","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"b1ab5de74c","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在国防战线上的胜利!","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"0711e67bee","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在土地改革战线上的胜利!","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"564a258427","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在镇压反革命战线上的胜利!","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"62079e283a","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在经济和财政战线上的胜利!","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"6a1fc76abd","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在文化和教育战线上的胜利!","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"038a0281b4","type":"paragraph","text":"祝我们在社会各界首先是知识分子的思想改造战线上的胜利!","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"a82f49c402","type":"paragraph","text":"我还要祝我们在新开辟的一条战线上的胜利，这就是号召我国全体人民和一切工作人员一致起来，大张旗鼓地，雷厉风行地，开展一个大规模的反对贪污、反对浪费、反对官僚主义的斗争，将这些旧社会遗留下来的污毒洗干净!","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"9ec3da73ea","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，我们在上述一切战线上，在一九五一年，都已取得了胜利，有许多是极其伟大的胜利。我们希望，经过我们的共同努力，所有这些工作，在一九五二年能够取得更大的胜利。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"},{"id":"fa117f8a3b","type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国万岁!","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de"}],"page":{"id":"bbbc505f32","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"69f423a2de","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}